  <time:MonthOfYear rdf:about="http://www.w3.org/ns/time/gregorian/January">
    <rdfs:label>January</rdfs:label>
    <skos:historyNote>A _class_ with the local-name January was present in the 2006 version of OWL-Time. &#13;
It was presented as an example of how DateTimeDescription could be specialized. &#13;
In the 2017 version of OWL-Time that class is deprecated, but this individual provided instead, in a separate namespace. </skos:historyNote>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="ru">Январь</skos:prefLabel>
